original: Brunnander, Theodor Adolf, kyrko-berde, Svanesund, f. 11/8/96 i Öh-remma, Älvsb. 1. G. 26 m. Käthe Maria Josume. Barn: Sven f. 29, Inger 30, Birgit 32. — Stud:ex. 14, teol. kand. 17. Kommin. i Fagereds past. 22, kyrkoh. i Myckleby fr. 34. Ordf. i Källsjö komm rstämma 25-35, i kyr-kost. o. skolråd 32-35, i Myckleby o. Torps kyrkost., i skolstyr.
translated: Brunnander, Theodor Adolf, church clerk, Svanesund, b. 11/8/96 in Öh-remma, Älvsborg. Married 26 in partnership with Käthe Maria Josume. Children: Sven b. 29, Inger b. 30, Birgit b. 32. - Studied: graduation exam 14, theology candidate 17. Curate in Fagereds parish 22, vicar in Myckleby from 34. Chairman of Källsjö commune council from 25-35, in the church council and school council from 32-35, in the church council of Myckleby and Torp, and on the school board.
